# Go project template
## Prerequisites
- gcloud cli

## Techniques
- Gin
- Graphql
- Firestore

## Start
- Create `.env` file
```
cp .env.local .env
```

- Login to google cloud
```
// Login google cloud
gcloud init
// Login firebase
docker compose run --rm firestore firebase login --no-localhost
```

- Start
```
make dev
```

## Scripts

```
// generate graphql from schemas
make graphql-gen
```